de: Third Amendment to the Memorandum of Understanding between the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of the Swiss Confederation and the Ministry of Regional Development, Construction and Communal Services of Ukraine, the Executive Committee of the Vinnitsa City Council, the Vinnitsa Public Utility "Vinnitsa Misk Teplo Energo" on the Granting of Technical and Financial Assistance for the Energy Efficiency Vinnitsa Project  - 19-12-2018 - Memorandum of Understanding zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und der Ukraine betreffend des Projekts «Energieeffizienz in Vinnitsa»
en: Third Amendment to the Memorandum of Understanding between the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of the Swiss Confederation and the Ministry of Regional Development, Construction and Communal Services of Ukraine, the Executive Committee of the Vinnitsa City Council, the Vinnitsa Public Utility "Vinnitsa Misk Teplo Energo" on the Granting of Technical and Financial Assistance for the Energy Efficiency Vinnitsa Project  - 19-12-2018 - Memorandum of Understanding between the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of the Swiss Confederation and the Ministry of Regional Development, Construction and Communal Services of Ukraine, the Executive Committee of the Vinnitsa City Council, the Vinnitsa Public Utility "Vinnitsa Misk Teplo Energo" on the Granting of Technical and Financial Assistance for the Energy Efficiency Vinnitsa Project
fr: Third Amendment to the Memorandum of Understanding between the State Secretariat for Economic Affairs of the Swiss Confederation and the Ministry of Regional Development, Construction and Communal Services of Ukraine, the Executive Committee of the Vinnitsa City Council, the Vinnitsa Public Utility "Vinnitsa Misk Teplo Energo" on the Granting of Technical and Financial Assistance for the Energy Efficiency Vinnitsa Project  - 19-12-2018 - Protocole d'entente entre la Suisse, représentée par le SECO, et l'Ukraine concernant le projet «efficience énergétique à Vinnitsa»
